videos.headline: Eastern Michigan QB powers in for 3-yard TD
videos.description: Eastern Michigan strikes first as Mike Glass III runs in a three-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Eastern Michign's Glass runs in his 2nd TD of the day
videos.description: Mike Glass III continues to dominate as he gets free for a  22-yard Eastern Michigan touchdown.

videos.headline: Toledo chips at the lead as Guadagni finds Thompson for 18-yard TD
videos.description: Mitchell Guadagni lobs it to Cody Thompson for a 18-yard Toledo touchdown.

videos.headline: Toledo's comeback falls short as they miss 2-pt conversion
videos.description: Toledo's come back falls short after Mitchell Guadagni runs in a 10-yard touchdown, but Toledo fails to convert the two-point conversions.
